1. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses distributed learning approaches such as federated learning and proposes an incentive mechanism to improve worker performance. 
2. cs.GT (Game Theory): The paper uses a Stackelberg game to model the interaction between the model owner and workers and obtain an equilibrium solution. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a mechanism to improve the performance of distributed learning, which is a key area of research in AI. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper discusses the challenges of distributed learning and proposes a mechanism to improve its performance. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a mechanism to control the performance of workers in a distributed learning system.
